  • Constructor Details

    • Job

      public Job​(java.lang.String message)
      Default constructor creates a representation of the current job. The job itself will have the message and Job ID transmitted to an assigned node.
      Parameters:
      message - this is the only variable that needs to be passed to construct the Within this constructor the LocalDateTime and DateTimeFormatter packages are utilised to construct a representation of the current time at the precise moment a job is instantiated, it is then converted to an integer and assigned as the arrival time.

    • Job
